taskr User Stories
==================

As a user,
I want to store tasks that need to be done
so that I can see them in the future

As a user,
I want to be able to see all my tasks in one place
so that I can choose what to do

As a user,
I want I want to be able to set at due date on my tasks
so that I can accomplish my tasks on time

As a user,
I want to set a priority to my tasks
So that I can choose what to do

As a user,
I want to set a category to my tasks
So that I can group the tasks together

As a user,
I want to be able to sort all my tasks by due date priority and category
so that I can better visualise all the tasks I have to do